## Summary of changes

**`src/overlay/sections/PositionOffsetDiagram.tsx`:**
- Added 4 `<UnitSelector>` instances вҖ” one next to each offset `EditableValue` (top, right, bottom, left)
- Each `UnitSelector` receives `options={availableUnits}` (which resolves to `POSITION_UNITS` = `["px", "%", "vw", "vh"]`)
- Each `UnitSelector` calls `onUnitChange("top"|"right"|"bottom"|"left", unit)` on change, wiring to the existing conversion logic in `PositionSection`
- `conversionHint` passed through for conversion tooltips
- `embedded` mode for compact rendering within the diagram
- Removed the now-redundant `suffix` prop from `EditableValue`
- Widened left/right columns from `40px` вҶ’ `56px` to fit the unit pill

